Installation of AWS CLI is now a bit different:

Get the package from AWS

curl "https://awscli.amazonaws.com/awscli-exe-linux-x86_64.zip" -o "awscliv2.zip"

You may need to install unzip
sudo apt install unzip

---> unzip awscliv2.zip

install AWS CLI
---> sudo ./aws/install

check version

aws --version
